                                  <button 
                                     onClick={() => handleNavigateToStock(stock.code, stock.name)}
                                     className="flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 hover:text-indigo-700 transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest bg-indigo-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-indigo-100"
                                  >
                                     深度量化分析 <ArrowRight className="w-3 h-3" />
                                  </button>
                               </div>
                            </td>
                         </tr>
                      ))}
                   </tbody>
                </table>
             </div>
          </div>

          {/* Explanatory Footer */}
          <div className="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center py-10">
             <div className="flex items-center gap-3 px-6 py-3 bg-white rounded-full border border-slate-200 text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">
                <Rocket className="w-4 h-4 text-rose-500" /> 起爆：3-5日合力正向极致共振
             </div>
             <div className="flex items-center gap-3 px-6 py-3 bg-white rounded-full border border-slate-200 text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">
                <Lock className="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500" /> 锁筹：主力高比例控盘，拒绝回调
